com.incadencecorp.coalesce.common.helpers

Class DocumentProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.incadencecorp.coalesce.common.helpers.DocumentProperties

  • public class DocumentProperties
extends Object
    Provides access to the properties of a file. If the file is an OpenXML document it will provide access to the internal properties of the document.
    Author:
    InCadence

      • initialize

        public boolean initialize(String fullFilename)
                   throws com.drew.imaging.ImageProcessingException,
                          IOException,
                          org.jdom2.JDOMException,
                          CoalesceCryptoException
        Initializes a DocumentProperties from a file without encryption. If the file is an OpenXml file type then the internal Core properties are extracted. If the file is an image then the properties of the image are extracted and a thumbnail version of the file is generated.
        Parameters:
        fullFilename - the full path and filename of the file.
        Returns:
        True if successful.
        Throws:
        com.drew.imaging.ImageProcessingException
        IOException
        org.jdom2.JDOMException
        CoalesceCryptoException

      • initialize

        public boolean initialize(String fullFilename,
                          boolean encrypted)
                   throws com.drew.imaging.ImageProcessingException,
                          IOException,
                          org.jdom2.JDOMException,
                          CoalesceCryptoException
        Initializes a DocumentProperties from a file without encryption. If the file is an OpenXml file type then the internal Core properties are extracted. If the file is an image then the properties of the image are extracted and a thumbnail version of the file is generated.
        Parameters:
        fullFilename - the full path and filename of the file.
        encrypted - Whether the file needs to be decrypted or not.
        Returns:
        True if successful.
        Throws:
        com.drew.imaging.ImageProcessingException
        IOException
        org.jdom2.JDOMException
        CoalesceCryptoException
